OL,3,CHuge fire near Glasgow Central station
OL,4,Ccauses major travel disruption
OL,6,FA fire has broken out near Glasgow
OL,7,FCentral railway station, causing major
OL,8,Ftravel disruption.
OL,10,FDozens of trains were cancelled on
OL,11,FSunday evening following the blaze at
OL,12,Fa vape shop in Union Street.
OL,14,FNational Rail said the station will be
OL,15,Fclosed "until further notice" as crews
OL,16,Fcontinued to tackle the fire five
OL,17,Fhours after it began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
