OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773079566
OL,3,CHuge fire near Glasgow Central station
OL,4,Ccauses major travel disruption
OL,6,FNo trains will run to or from the high-
OL,7,Flevel platforms at Scotland's busiest
OL,8,Fstation, and trains that run through
OL,9,Fthe low-level platforms will not call
OL,10,Fat Glasgow Central.
OL,12,FNetwork Rail said the station will
OL,13,Fremain closed on Monday morning and
OL,14,FNational Rail expects disruption to
OL,15,Fcontinue on routes to, from and
OL,16,Fthrough the station throughout Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
