OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773079566
OL,3,CHuge fire near Glasgow Central station
OL,4,Ccauses major travel disruption
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney said in a
OL,7,Fpost on X: "I am deeply concerned
OL,8,Fabout the fire near Glasgow Central
OL,9,FStation tonight and very grateful to
OL,10,Fall of the emergency services who are
OL,11,Fresponding.
OL,13,F"Please continue to follow travel
OL,14,Fguidance, avoid the area and stay
OL,15,Fsafe."
OL,17,FPaul Sweeney, Labour MSP for Glasgow,
OL,18,Fsaid the building ` which housed the
OL,19,Fvape shop where the fire started ` had
OL,20,Fpartially collapsed.
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@AOUwD@FO]
