OL,3,CHuge fire near Glasgow Central station
OL,4,Ccauses major travel disruption
OL,6,FIn a post on X, he said the building
OL,7,Fdates back to 1851.
OL,9,F"Sadly the building has now partially
OL,10,Fcollapsed. I hope the fire can be
OL,11,Fcontained. The corner of the Forsyth
OL,12,FBuilding, as well as the Caledonian
OL,13,FChambers and Central Hotel seem
OL,14,Funaffected," Mr Sweeney said.
OL,16,F"It's a massive blow to Union Street
OL,17,Fwith the restoration of the Egyptian
OL,18,FHalls in prospect."
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@LO]xD@AOUzD@SO]
