OL,3,CHuge fire near Glasgow Central station
OL,4,Ccauses major travel disruption
OL,6,FIn a statement at 8.30pm, a Scottish
OL,7,FFire and Rescue Service spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid firefighters continued to work at
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,FIt said there were no reported
OL,12,Fcasualties.
OL,14,FSome ticket acceptance is in place,
OL,15,Fwith Avanti West Coast passengers able
OL,16,Fto use their tickets at no extra cost
OL,17,Fon LNER services between Edinburgh and
OL,18,FLondon King's Cross.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
